column2: The Lacustrine Republic & Muscogee Council reject authority of the Capitol.

The Native Americans around the Great Lakes and the Cis-Missisippi Peoples have rejected the authority of the Capitol in Yeni Rum. A serious threat to the stability of the Republic, the Protector-Elect has declared a National Emergency and mobilized the Federal Military Forces in order to bring these anarchist catharian citizens in line again.

Despite the attempts of integration by giving Natives in Catharia citizenship, pressure from prior colonialism and the current wave of settlers the Americans still are treated as a second class citizen. This has prompted a lot of influential leaders within the populace to emerge speaking about their own identity within this Republic seperate from Catharian.
But in the end we are all Cathar

The Republic of Catharia has a proud heritage of a lot of culture, however it has caused a lot of issues when it comes to administration and governance of the country as there is no one true language spoken by all. A lot of the settlers are promoting that we adopt the Turkish Creole known as Catharian.
The Federal Language will be Cathar.
